    "causal_summary": "sk-design modes currently have no shared evidence contracts for three gaps that two independent Hallmark adoption research syntheses converged on as their highest-confidence findings: (1) there is no provider-neutral schema for describing owned assets without hotlinking or bundling third-party binaries; (2) there is no semantic vocabulary connecting motion \"character\" intent to sk-design's existing timing/easing bands; (3) the `MotionSystem` detector already produces motion evidence, but the v3 DESIGN.md schema has no output section for it — the gap is output, not detection",
